{"tid":1818329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"越南徵地糾紛，最少3名警員及1名村民死亡","createTime":"2020-01-09T22:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T23:33:02.000Z","uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74826d6fb5a6f7d4892ae4ecc447ee6d7f51338d","tid":1818329,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T22:49:27.000Z","msg":"越南徵地糾紛釀警民衝突2020/01/10 <br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】越南首都河內附近一條村，因徵地糾紛引發警民衝突，最少3名警員及1名村民死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲村民投降，勿衝擊封鎖線，但高處不停有爆炸及燃燒物投下，有村民稱當局強徵了47公頃土地，作為軍方興建機場及旗下流動通訊企業營運所用，但他們數代人都使用同一片土地，並且多年來向政府繳足稅款和費用；當地公安部指反抗村民用手榴彈、汽油彈及刀等襲擊警員，有村民則指有人只是想逃走，但遭警員粗暴對待及拘捕。土地糾紛已持續多年，2017年一度有30多名警員被脅持為人質，最後警方釋放被捕村民，事件暫時解決。"},{"pid":"495c01295db740d0d9c0cedd8c1c2920cdc9f486","tid":1818329,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T22:50:01.000Z","msg":"手榴彈，脅持人質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45e77be1cd933b8117882388afa3d8faeb77049","tid":1818329,"uid":75655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T22:54:14.000Z","msg":"香港 be water 最有效，唔好戀戰，唔好烏克蘭佔領，黃色經濟圈最有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0118a1f774f5cc7ce07ecf55071c7959e1c2615a","tid":1818329,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c45e77be1cd933b8117882388afa3d8faeb77049","tid":1818329,"uid":75655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T22:54:14.000Z","msg":"香港 be water 最有效，唔好戀戰，唔好烏克蘭佔領，黃色經濟圈最有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:05:16.000Z","msg":"你都幾勤力"},{"pid":"e2ccafb1e339eac651b9c0b23dfc4a627c95b408","tid":1818329,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0118a1f774f5cc7ce07ecf55071c7959e1c2615a","tid":1818329,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":